I’m trying to get this template code to run on a little swerve workhorse chassis, but when I idle it, it sounds like this.

There’s no visible movement, but I know the sound comes from the turning motors vibrating.

Using 2022 code, we were able to implement a function like this:

image1115×814 42.7 KB

but after updating gradle and vendordeps to 2023, this kind of implementation just makes everything significantly worse.

If you know of a good way to fix this, please let me know. Thank you!
